  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Supporting the Greek Authorities in Managing the National Reception System for Asylum Seekers and Vulnerable Migrants (SMS)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Building upon its extensive experience and lessons learned throughout the past years and especially during 2019, IOM continues to support the Greek authorities in the daily management of the open accommodation sites by providing holistic site management support assistance (SMS), including protection and non-formal education (NFE) components, and pursuing the streamlining of a harmonized SMS model across all sites.</narrative>
  </description>
